robertianburns.cryptarchsarchive

Class HeaderGridView.HeaderViewGridAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • robertianburns.cryptarchsarchive.HeaderGridView.HeaderViewGridAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.widget.Adapter, android.widget.Filterable, android.widget.ListAdapter, android.widget.WrapperListAdapter
    Enclosing class:
    HeaderGridView

    private static class HeaderGridView.HeaderViewGridAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.widget.WrapperListAdapter, android.widget.Filterable
    ListAdapter used when a HeaderGridView has header views. This ListAdapter wraps another one and also keeps track of the header views and their associated data objects.

    This is intended as a base class; you will probably not need to use this class directly in your own code.
